Build requirements:
  cmake >=3.0.0
  flex >=2.5.31
  bison
  Recent GCC
  Recent glibc
  (optional) pkg-config
  (optional) zlib
  (optional) libpng

Build instructions:
  $ mkdir -p build && cd build
  $ cmake .. # append -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=(directory) if you want to
             # customize the install directory
             # append -DWITH_LIBPNG_SOURCE=OFF if you want to use an installed
             # version of libpng
  $ make
  # make install
